parameters.name: model_id
parameters.description: Seller SKU of the model, model_sku length restriction needs to be no more than 100 characters

parameters.name: seller_stock
parameters.description: Seller stock {Please notice that stock=0,selling_stock=0 means out of stock. Please don't fill the seller_stock>0 when your real stock reached 0}

parameters.name: dimension
parameters.description: The dimension of the model. If don't set the dimension of this model, will use the dimension of item by default

parameters.name: package_length
parameters.description: The length of package for this model, the unit is CM

parameters.name: package_width
parameters.description: The width of package for this model, the unit is CM

parameters.name: package_height
parameters.description: The height of package for this model, the unit is CM

parameters.name: is_pre_order
parameters.description: Whether the model is pre order

parameters.name: days_to_ship
parameters.description: Days to ship. Please set the days_to_ship longer than pre_order_days if it's a pre-order item
